I don't know if they really were, but I recall when I was wee the screens were somewhat cruel to you, at least that's how I felt about them.

the songs I used are by Jack Stauber, "On" and "Viator"

I think it's pretty clear, but like, you maybe shouldn't drive after popping a lukewarm one without the boys.
